      "body": "If you don't receive any transactions with the wallet, you could just send the entire balance to a new wallet and use that new wallet file from now on. That's not really ideal from a privacy standpoint, but it's a solution. Alternatively export all relevant private keys and import them into a new wallet, leaving those you don't need behind.\n",
