      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "body": "You could try -zapwallettx. It will remove all transactions from the wallet and rescan them from the block chain. This may make the wallet smaller. After that you could compact the bdb file like this to get rid of empty space:\n\n``` bash\ncp wallet.dat wallet.dat.backup\ndb4.8_dump wallet.dat | db4.8_load wallet.dat.new\nmv wallet.dat.new wallet.dat\n```\n",
